description:
The PSP is one of the greatest handheld consoles of all time, with a ton of incredible games! Join TVGS as I list and discuss ten of the most over looked and forgotten PSP rpgs on the system. Many lesser known and under appreciated rpgs released for the Playstation Portable so let me know your most obscure, lesser known and underrated PSP games down below!

Join us on Discord - https://discord.gg/aP2wbhfS4U

All of my PSP videos can be found here - https://tinyurl.com/psp-video-list
